        "title": {
          "ja": "作る成果物を判断する",
          "en": "Decide the product being built"
        },
        "title_key": "documentsPage.brief.requirements.title",
        "detail": {
          "ja": "タスク管理表に必要な機能と、対象外を確認します。",
          "en": "Confirm the required features and out-of-scope items for the task management table."
        },
        "detail_key": "documentsPage.brief.requirements.detail",
        "summary": {
          "ja": "対象成果物はSTEP 1-14実践レッスンのタスク管理表です。ブラウザで開けること、タスク追加、空タイトルの防止、担当者・優先度・期限・状態の記録、todo/doing/doneの移動、件数表示、ローカル保存、テスト、E2E、CI、運用マニフェストが求められています。",
          "en": "The target product is the STEP 1-14 practical lesson task management table. It must open in a browser, add tasks, reject empty titles, record owner, priority, due date, and status, move tasks across todo/doing/done, show counts, keep browser-local data, and include tests, E2E, CI, and operation manifests."
        },
        "summary_key": "documentsPage.brief.requirements.summary",
        "action": {
          "ja": "この成果物が「タスク管理表」として必要な機能を満たしているかを確認します。認証、共有ストレージ、サーバーAPI、課金、外部連携、個人情報は対象外として扱います。",
          "en": "Check whether the product satisfies the task management table requirements. Treat authentication, shared storage, server APIs, billing, external integrations, and personal data as out of scope."
        },
        "action_key": "documentsPage.brief.requirements.action",
        "status": "ready",
        "metric_label_key": "documentsPage.brief.metric.outcome",
        "metric_value": "タスク管理表",
